00:13:28.140 --> 00:13:29.610
ALICE MARIE JOHNSON: Yes.

00:13:29.610 --> 00:13:30.693
ANDREA JAMES: And you're--

00:13:30.693 --> 00:13:32.110
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:13:32.110 --> 00:13:33.212
ALICE MARIE JOHNSON: Yes.

00:13:33.212 --> 00:13:35.670
ANDREA JAMES: You were a mother,
and you know directly what

00:13:35.670 --> 00:13:39.810
