00:15:17.400 --> 00:15:19.950
and then drawing it back.

00:15:19.950 --> 00:15:22.080
Because we all had so
much hope that that

00:15:22.080 --> 00:15:23.580
was going to come
through, because I

00:15:23.580 --> 00:15:25.300
knew I fit the criteria.

00:15:25.300 --> 00:15:28.560
But as you see, I'm left
behind and I'm still here.

00:15:28.560 --> 00:15:31.320
And this is what I
want to say to Google.

00:15:31.320 --> 00:15:35.790
Google is a company that
has been greatly blessed.

00:15:35.790 --> 00:15:39.480
To whom much is given,
much is required.

00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:43.170
When you use your
voice, people listen.

00:15:43.170 --> 00:15:48.720
When you champion a cause,
our leadership listens.

00:15:48.720 --> 00:15:52.360
