brother's or sister's keeper?

00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:57.070
And I say to you to that,
if not you, then who?

00:15:57.070 --> 00:15:59.490
If not now, then when?

00:15:59.490 --> 00:16:01.470
I don't want to die in prison.

00:16:01.470 --> 00:16:04.530
To say later may
be too late for me.

00:16:04.530 --> 00:16:05.900
I'm already 62.

00:16:05.900 --> 00:16:08.130
I've already spent
two decades in prison.

00:16:08.130 --> 00:16:13.230
So I believe that as
responsible citizens we do

00:16:13.230 --> 00:16:16.440
have a responsibility
to each other.

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:17.220
We do.

00:16:17.220 --> 00:16:20.100
It is not just a
social issue that you

00:16:20.100 --> 00:16:22.470
put on an agenda that
sounds good on paper.

00:16:22.470 --> 00:16:25.680
It's something you
have to take to heart.

00:16:25.680 --> 00:16:28.500
When you see me and so
many others like me,

00:16:28.500 --> 00:16:31.680
you see I'm just a
representative, a very small

00:16:31.680 --> 00:16:33.750
representative.

00:16:33.750 --> 00:16:36.390
But there's many
more just like me.

00:16:36.390 --> 00:16:38.550
And I don't believe
that the public is safe

00:16:38.550 --> 00:16:41.160
because I'm here.

00:16:41.160 --> 00:16:44.690
I'm non-violent, and I've
already spent 20 years.

00:16:44.690 --> 00:16:49.280
And I've had 100% clear conduct.

00:16:49.280 --> 00:16:53.800
