00:43:22.620 --> 00:43:24.600
And I was raised
underneath my grandparents.

00:43:24.600 --> 00:43:27.240
So when my mother went
to prison, obviously,

00:43:27.240 --> 00:43:29.550
it was either she gives
me to somebody else,

00:43:29.550 --> 00:43:32.280
or I'd be in a
foster home, or just

00:43:32.280 --> 00:43:34.380
under the care of somebody else.

00:43:34.380 --> 00:43:37.890
So she gave power of
attorney to my grandparents.

00:43:37.890 --> 00:43:41.790
And in that time, it was
as if the relationship

00:43:41.790 --> 00:43:44.010
between my mother
and my father and I

00:43:44.010 --> 00:43:46.260
had been transferred
