00:59:43.270 --> 00:59:48.280
to pass legislation that would
incarcerate people for profit.

00:59:48.280 --> 00:59:50.450
And so I don't want
anyone to think that,

00:59:50.450 --> 00:59:52.870
hey, these are people who
