01:39:48.810 --> 01:39:51.860
Not me, but the inside of me.

01:39:51.860 --> 01:39:54.830
They say I act out
because of my ADHD.

01:39:54.830 --> 01:39:56.380
I'm going to be me.

01:39:56.380 --> 01:39:58.020
Learn to sit up like a baby.

01:39:58.020 --> 01:40:00.290
Better yet, trying
to come out a cocoon,

01:40:00.290 --> 01:40:02.300
hopefully one day, or maybe.

01:40:02.300 --> 01:40:04.640
Picking that cheese,
like a baby mice,

01:40:04.640 --> 01:40:07.310
like a caged bird
screaming for food.

01:40:07.310 --> 01:40:11.270
Is it bad that my mind seeks
the gates of hell, or wonders

01:40:11.270 --> 01:40:12.820
for a black night?

01:40:12.820 --> 01:40:15.620
Why can't I have
someone hold me tight?

01:40:15.620 --> 01:40:17.690
I look at my reflection,
and yet my body

01:40:17.690 --> 01:40:21.080
starts to feel cold, like
a polar bear in winter

01:40:21.080 --> 01:40:23.340
but a vampire at night.

01:40:23.340 --> 01:40:26.130
Katrina washing people
away and I'm trying

01:40:26.130 --> 01:40:27.610
to find that secret get away.

01:40:27.610 --> 01:40:28.110
Thank you.

